OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Remaining dry overnight
OL,7,Fbut clouding over across Lothians and
OL,8,FBorders. Dumfries and Galloway will be
OL,9,Fclear with some patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FOvernight low cloud mostly
OL,12,Fburning off in the east, but may
OL,13,Flinger along parts of the east coast.
OL,14,FOtherwise dry and sunny. Becoming
OL,15,Fwarm, but cooler along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
