OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry and settled into the weekend with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunshine. Low cloud may be
OL,8,Fslow to clear eastern coastal
OL,9,Fdistricts. Warm inland, but cooler
OL,10,Fnear the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
